    <title>Java 基础</title>
    <url>/2021/09/18/Java-%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="特点"><a href="#特点" class="headerlink" title="特点"></a>特点</h1><ol>
<li><p>面向对象：封装、继承、多态</p>
</li>
<li><p>平台无关性：（JVM实现） </p>
</li>
<li><p>编译与解释并存    </p>
</li>
</ol>
<h1 id="JVM-JDK-JRE"><a href="#JVM-JDK-JRE" class="headerlink" title="JVM/JDK/JRE"></a>JVM/JDK/JRE</h1><p>JVM：运行java字节码的虚拟机</p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/lingzhexi/blogImage/raw/master/2021/09/22/202109221132375.png" alt="img"></p>
<h2 id="字节码"><a href="#字节码" class="headerlink" title="字节码"></a>字节码</h2><p>JVM可以理解的代码叫 <code>字节码</code> （.class 文件）</p>
<h2 id="Java程序到源代码运行"><a href="#Java程序到源代码运行" class="headerlink" title="Java程序到源代码运行"></a>Java程序到源代码运行</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/lingzhexi/blogImage/raw/master/2021/09/22/202109221123604.png" alt="img"></p>
<h2 id="编译和解释型语言："><a href="#编译和解释型语言：" class="headerlink" title="编译和解释型语言："></a>编译和解释型语言：</h2><p>Java 编写的程序需要先经过编译步骤，生成字节码（*.class 文件），这种字节码必须由 Java 解释器来解释执行</p>
<h1 id="基本语法"><a href="#基本语法" class="headerlink" title="基本语法"></a>基本语法</h1><h2 id="字符型常量和字符串常量"><a href="#字符型常量和字符串常量" class="headerlink" title="字符型常量和字符串常量"></a>字符型常量和字符串常量</h2><ol>
<li><strong>含义</strong>：字符型常量相当于一个整型值（ASCII值）可以参加表达式运算；字符串常量：表示一个地址（内存中的位置）</li>
<li><strong>内存大小</strong>：字符型常量占两个字节，字符串常量占若干个字节</li>
</ol>
<p>char 的包装类 <code>**Character**</code> 成员变量 <code>**Character.SIZE = 16**</code> 单位 <code>**bits**</code> ，除以8 (<code>**1byte = 8bits**</code>) 得到 2字节</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>No.</th>
<th>数据类型</th>
<th>大小/位<bits></th>
<th>可表示数据范围</th>
<th>默认值</th>
<th>包装类</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>1</td>
<td>byte（字节型）</td>
<td>8</td>
<td>-128~127</td>
<td>0</td>
<td>Byte</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2</td>
<td>short（短整型）</td>
<td>16</td>
<td>-32768~32767</td>
<td>0</td>
<td>Short</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>3</td>
<td>int（整型）</td>
<td>32</td>
<td>-2147483648~2147483647</td>
<td>0</td>
<td>Integer</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>4</td>
<td>long（长整型）</td>
<td>64</td>
<td>-9223372036854775808~9223372036854775807</td>
<td>0</td>
<td>Long</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>5</td>
<td>float（单精度）</td>
<td>32</td>
<td>-3.4E38~3.4E38</td>
<td>0.0</td>
<td>Float</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>6</td>
<td>double（双精度）</td>
<td>64</td>
<td>-1.7E308~1.7E308</td>
<td>0.0</td>
<td>Double</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>7</td>
<td>char（字符）</td>
<td>16</td>
<td>0~255</td>
<td>‘\u0000’</td>
<td>Character</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>8</td>
<td>boolean（布尔）</td>
<td>-</td>
<td>true或false</td>
<td>false</td>
<td>Boolean</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="二进制"><a href="#二进制" class="headerlink" title="二进制"></a>二进制</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/lingzhexi/blogImage/raw/master/2021/09/22/202109221123327.png" alt="img"></p>
<h2 id="基本类型和引用类型"><a href="#基本类型和引用类型" class="headerlink" title="基本类型和引用类型"></a>基本类型和引用类型</h2><h3 id="存储位置"><a href="#存储位置" class="headerlink" title="存储位置"></a>存储位置</h3><h4 id="基本变量类型"><a href="#基本变量类型" class="headerlink" title="基本变量类型"></a>基本变量类型</h4><ul>
<li>在方法中定义的非全局基本数据类型变量的具体内容是存储在栈中的</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="引用变量类型"><a href="#引用变量类型" class="headerlink" title="引用变量类型"></a>引用变量类型</h4><ul>
<li>只要是引用数据类型变量，其具体内容都是存放在堆中的，而栈中存放的是其具体内容所在内存的地址<br><em>ps:通过变量地址可以找到变量的具体内容，就如同通过房间号可以找到房间一般</em></li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Main</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//基本数据类型</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">double</span> d=<span class="number">1.2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       </span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//引用数据类型</span></span><br><span class="line">       String str=<span class="string">&quot;helloworld&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://gitee.com/lingzhexi/blogImage/raw/master/2021/09/22/202109221124197.png" alt="img"></p>
<h2 id="Java内存模型"><a href="#Java内存模型" class="headerlink" title="Java内存模型"></a>Java内存模型</h2><p>JMM</p>
<h2 id="注释"><a href="#注释" class="headerlink" title="注释"></a>注释</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/lingzhexi/blogImage/raw/master/2021/09/22/202109221127159.png" alt="img"></p>
<h2 id="Java-中的关键字"><a href="#Java-中的关键字" class="headerlink" title="Java 中的关键字"></a>Java 中的关键字</h2><p>标识符—关键字</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th><strong>分类</strong></th>
<th><strong>关键字</strong></th>
<th></th>
<th></th>
<th></th>
<th></th>
<th></th>
<th></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>访问控制</td>
<td>private</td>
<td>protected</td>
<td>public</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>类，方法和变量修饰符</td>
<td>abstract</td>
<td>class</td>
<td>extends</td>
<td>final</td>
<td>implements</td>
<td>interface</td>
<td>native</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td>new</td>
<td>static</td>
<td>strictfp</td>
<td>synchronized</td>
<td>transient</td>
<td>volatile</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>程序控制</td>
<td>break</td>
<td>continue</td>
<td>return</td>
<td>do</td>
<td>while</td>
<td>if</td>
<td>else</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td>for</td>
<td>instanceof</td>
<td>switch</td>
<td>case</td>
<td>default</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>错误处理</td>
<td>try</td>
<td>catch</td>
<td>throw</td>
<td>throws</td>
<td>finally</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>包相关</td>
<td>import</td>
<td>package</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>基本类型</td>
<td>boolean</td>
<td>byte</td>
<td>char</td>
<td>double</td>
<td>float</td>
<td>int</td>
<td>long</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td>short</td>
<td>null</td>
<td>true</td>
<td>false</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>变量引用</td>
<td>super</td>
<td>this</td>
<td>void</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>保留字</td>
<td>goto</td>
<td>const</td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="自增、自减"><a href="#自增、自减" class="headerlink" title="自增、自减"></a>自增、自减</h2><p>符号在前就先加/减，符号在后就后加/减</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//符号在前就先加/减，符号在后就后加/减</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//赋值</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> a = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> b = <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        ++a;<span class="comment">//自增 运算 ++a =a+1  a++ =a+1</span></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a);<span class="comment">//2</span></span><br><span class="line">        a++;<span class="comment">//自增 运算</span></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a);<span class="comment">//3</span></span><br><span class="line">        b = ++a;<span class="comment">//自增  赋值 b = (a+1);</span></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(b);<span class="comment">//4</span></span><br><span class="line">        b = a++;<span class="comment">//自增  赋值 b = a; a= a+1;</span></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(b);<span class="comment">//4</span></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a);<span class="comment">//5</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="continue、break、和return-的区别"><a href="#continue、break、和return-的区别" class="headerlink" title="continue、break、和return 的区别"></a>continue、break、和return 的区别</h2><p>循环结构体，当循环条件不满足或者循环次数达到要求是，循环会正常结束，有时需要自定义。</p>
<ol>
<li><p>continue: 跳出当前循环，继续下一次循环</p>
</li>
<li><p>break：跳出整个循环，继续执行循环下面的语句</p>
</li>
<li><p>return：跳出整个方法，结束方法运行</p>
</li>
<li><ol>
<li>return  ：直接使用返回方法，没有返回值函数方法</li>
<li>return value：有返回值函数方法</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="和-equals-比较"><a href="#和-equals-比较" class="headerlink" title="== 和 equals 比较"></a>== 和 equals 比较</h2><p>基本类型比较值，引用类型比较地址</p>
<p>java 只有值传递，本质上来讲==就是比较值，只是引用变量存的值是对象的地址</p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/lingzhexi/blogImage/raw/master/2021/09/22/202109221124265.png" alt="img"></p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/lingzhexi/blogImage/raw/master/2021/09/22/202109221124980.png" alt="img"></p>
<h2 id="哈希值"><a href="#哈希值" class="headerlink" title="哈希值"></a>哈希值</h2><p>String 的HashCode</p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/lingzhexi/blogImage/raw/master/2021/09/22/202109221124091.png" alt="img"></p>
<h2 id="变量"><a href="#变量" class="headerlink" title="变量"></a>变量</h2><blockquote>
<p>type  identifier = value,[ identifier[= value] …] ;</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><p>类变量：独立于方法之外的变量，用 static 修饰。</p>
</li>
<li><p>实例变量：独立于方法之外的变量，不过没有 static 修饰。</p>
</li>
<li><p>局部变量：类的方法中的变量。    </p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/lingzhexi/blogImage/raw/master/2021/09/22/202109221125117.png" alt="img"></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">	<span class="comment">// 使用增加方法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">add</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">int</span> a = <span class="number">0</span>;   <span class="comment">// 3</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">int</span> b = <span class="number">1</span>;   <span class="comment">// 4</span></span><br><span class="line">       System.out.println( a+b );  <span class="comment">//1</span></span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment">// 调用方法 a = 3 b =4 进行加法运算</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="function"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">addArg</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> a, <span class="keyword">int</span> b)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       System.out.println(a + b);</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment">// 主方法 程序执行的入口</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       addArg(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>);</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
